Here is my first map !
This map is :
-fun (I hope)
-fast (rounds will not be long, you will frag immediatly)
-small (800Ko)

This map isn't :
-for spawnkillers (you will not see the ennemy spawn)
-for non-spawnkillers (your bullets will go throught the metal wall)
-for kikoololasv (you will not have the time to tk, noob !)


Ladders are invisible, i had a problem with their texture.



Please leave your comments and tips, that will help me for my next map :)
